  'layers'
  'layers.0'
  'layers.1'
  'layers.2'

--- to(dtype=float64) 测试 ---
Python list 容器: 子模块参数 dtype = torch.float32
nn.ModuleList 容器: 子模块参数 dtype = torch.float64

⚠️ Python list 中的 Linear 层的 weight 仍为 float32！
   因为 model.to(dtype) 没有递归到 Python list 中的模块。

<cell id="cell-26"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type>**关键结论**：

| 操作 | Python list | nn.ModuleList |
|------|-------------|---------------|
| `parameters()` | ❌ 0 个参数 | ✅ 6 个参数 |
| `named_modules()` | ❌ 不包含子模块 | ✅ 递归可见 |
| `model.to(dtype)` | ❌ 子模块不迁移 | ✅ 全部迁移 |
| `state_dict()` | ❌ 不保存 | ✅ 全部保存 |
| `model.cuda()` | ❌ 子模块留在 CPU | ✅ 全部移到 GPU |</cell id="cell-26">
<cell id="cell-27"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type>### 实验 2：Sequential 的切片、索引与运算</cell id="cell-27">
<cell id="cell-28"># 构建测试 Sequential
seq = nn.Sequential(
    nn.Linear(8, 16),    # 索引 0
    nn.ReLU(),           # 索引 1
    nn.Linear(16, 32),   # 索引 2
    nn.ReLU(),           # 索引 3
    nn.Linear(32, 10),   # 索引 4
)
print("原始 Sequential:")
print(seq)

# === 整数索引 ===
print("\n=== 整数索引 ===")
print(f"seq[0]:  {seq[0]}")
print(f"seq[-1]: {seq[-1]}")
print(f"seq[2]:  {seq[2]}")

# === 切片（返回新的 Sequential）===
print("\n=== 切片 ===")
subset = seq[1:3]
print(f"seq[1:3]: {subset}")
print(f"  类型: {type(subset).__name__}")
print(f"  长度: {len(subset)}")

# 负数切片
print(f"\nseq[-2:]: {seq[-2:]}")

# === append ===
print("\n=== append ===")
seq.append(nn.Softmax(dim=-1))
print(f"append Softmax 后长度: {len(seq)}")
print(f"  seq[-1]: {seq[-1]}")

# === insert ===
print("\n=== insert ===")
seq.insert(2, nn.Dropout(0.5))
print(f"insert Dropout 在索引 2 后:")
for i, (name, mod) in enumerate(seq.named_children()):
    print(f"  {name}: {mod}")

# === __add__ / __iadd__ ===
print("\n=== Sequential + Sequential ===")
seq_a = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(10, 20), nn.ReLU())
seq_b = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(20, 30), nn.ReLU())
seq_combined = seq_a + seq_b
print(f"seq_a + seq_b: 长度 {len(seq_combined)}")
for name, mod in seq_combined.named_children():
    print(f"  {name}: {mod}")

# === __mul__（重复串联）===
print(f"\n=== Sequential * n ===")
seq_triple = seq_a * 3
print(f"seq_a * 3: 长度 {len(seq_triple)}")
for name, mod in seq_triple.named_children():
    print(f"  {name}: {mod}")</cell id="cell-28">

