  conv: Conv1d(1, 1, kernel_size=(3,), stride=(1,), padding=(1,))
experts keys: ['linear', 'conv']

=== 动态添加 expert ===
experts keys: ['linear', 'conv', 'mlp']
mlp 是否在 named_modules 中: True

=== 动态替换 ===
替换前 linear: Linear(in_features=10, out_features=10, bias=True)
替换后 linear: Linear(in_features=10, out_features=10, bias=False)

=== 动态删除 ===
删除 conv 后 keys: ['linear', 'mlp']
conv 是否还在 named_modules 中: False

=== pop 操作 ===
pop mlp: Sequential(
  (0): Linear(in_features=10, out_features=20, bias=True)
  (1): ReLU()
  (2): Linear(in_features=20, out_features=10, bias=True)
)
剩余 keys: ['linear']

