  backbone.0.bias                           shape=[32]
  head.fc.weight                            shape=[16, 32]
  head.fc.bias                              shape=[16]
  branches.0.weight                         shape=[8, 16]
  branches.0.bias                           shape=[8]
  branches.1.weight                         shape=[8, 16]
  branches.1.bias                           shape=[8]
  adapters.scale.weight                     shape=[8, 8]
  adapters.scale.bias                       shape=[8]
  adapters.shift.weight                     shape=[8, 8]
  adapters.shift.bias                       shape=[8]
  biases.0                                  shape=[8]
  biases.1                                  shape=[8]

=== 规则总结 ===
  Sequential (自动编号):  backbone.0.weight, backbone.1 等
  Sequential (命名 key):   head.fc.weight, head.act 等
  ModuleList:              branches.0.weight, branches.1 等
  ModuleDict:              adapters.scale.weight, adapters.shift 等
  ParameterList:           biases.0, biases.1（直接参数，无子属性）

